---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout>
<!-- HERO -->
      <section class="hero hero-small">
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="section-badge">Information</span>
            <h1>Frequently asked questions before a first visit</h1>
            <p class="hero-lead">Common questions about confidentiality, treatment approach, costs, and what to expect during your appointment at Mind Grace Clinic.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ SECTIONS -->
      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="content-narrow">
            
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Confidentiality</h2>
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-1">
                  <span>Are sessions confidential?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-1" hidden>
                  <p>Yes. All information shared during consultations is strictly confidential and used only for your care and appointment coordination. The only exceptions are rare situations where there is an immediate risk to your safety or others', where we may need to contact emergency services or relevant authorities.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-2">
                  <span>Who will have access to my records?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-2" hidden>
                  <p>Only Dr. Anita Sharma and essential administrative staff involved in scheduling and billing have access to your records. We do not share information with third parties without your explicit written consent, except as required by law.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2 style="margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;">Medication and Treatment</h2>
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-3">
                  <span>Will I definitely be prescribed medication?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-3" hidden>
                  <p>Not necessarily. Medication is considered when clinically appropriate, but we also offer practical strategies, behavioural interventions, and therapeutic options. The treatment plan is personalized based on your specific needs, preferences, and clinical assessment.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-4">
                  <span>Do you provide therapy or only medication management?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-4" hidden>
                  <p>We offer both medication management and psychotherapy services. Depending on your needs, we may recommend individual therapy, family counseling, cognitive-behavioural techniques, or a combination of approaches alongside any medication if prescribed.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2 style="margin: 3rem 0 1.5rem;">Booking and Logistics</h2>
            <div class="accordion">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-5">
                  <span>How do I book an appointment?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-5" hidden>
                  <p>You can book an appointment by filling out our online booking form, calling us directly at +91 96678 63295, or sending a WhatsApp message. We'll confirm your appointment within 24–48 hours via your preferred contact method.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-6">
                  <span>What is the consultation fee?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-6" hidden>
                  <p>Initial psychiatric consultations typically range from ₹1500–₹2500 depending on the complexity and duration. Follow-up sessions and therapy have different rates. Please see our <a href="/fees.html">fees page</a> for detailed pricing information.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <button class="accordion-trigger" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-7">
                  <span>Do you accept insurance?</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-panel" id="faq-7" hidden>
                  <p>We accept most major health insurance plans that cover mental health services. Please check with your insurance provider about coverage for psychiatric consultations and therapy. We can provide receipts and documentation for insurance claims.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <section class="section-cta-center">
        <div class="container">
          <h2>Still have questions?</h2>
          <p>We're here to help clarify any concerns before your visit.</p>
          <div class="cta-group">
            <a href="/book.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book an Appointment</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/919667863295" class="btn btn-outline-light" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp Us</a>
            <a href="/contact.html" class="btn btn-outline-light">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
</BaseLayout>
